Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Human rights and the UN
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040bvz1
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 17 Dec 1978
Human rights and the not-quite United Nations - when oil comes before freedom. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.